code: import axios from'axios';const API_URL='http://localhost:5000/api';export const getDetections=async()=>{const response=await axios.get("".concat(API_URL,"/detections"));return response.data;};export const saveDetection=async detectionData=>{const response=await axios.post("".concat(API_URL,"/detections"),detectionData);return response.data;};export const deleteDetection=async id=>{const response=await axios.delete("".concat(API_URL,"/detections/").concat(id));return response.data;};
